          "reviewBody": "Excellent school, I am an alumni and both of my kids study here too. All previous comments of parents seems to make less sense, all who studied with me are well placed in their lives.\n\nThere is nothing wrong in being result oriented coz in real life there is insane world with high competition. If the parents are too protective with their children then i am sorry to those parents,  they need to know what’s out there.\n\nTeachers are trying to get best out of the kids, my child also receives many complaints from teacher but we need to take it positively and try to correct the child than to be over protective.\n\nDisclaimer:\nI am not a staff of this school and real parent and i love this school and its teacher/mgmt",
