          "reviewBody": "As a student of this school I have only great things to say about it . The teachers are amazing, the curriculum is really approving and each child is treated with care and no discrimination.\n\nIf you have any doubts please go and see the principal and she will put you at ease. I am blessed to have such kind and supporting teachers. Teachers are passionate about seeing their students succeed, they treat them as if they are their own children. No doubt that its one of the best  schools in Chennai.",
